  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为支付系统设计一个容灾机制，核心思路是责任链模式。当主支付通道失败时，自动切换到备用通道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PaymentSystem",
        "ChainHandler",
        "Handlers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，是用责任链实现多级降级。那整个系统边界怎么定？是画在应用内部还是包含外部服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PaymentSystem",
        "ExtA",
        "ExtB",
        "ExtC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "画成C4的容器图，PaymentSystem作为NestJS应用，内部包含API层、业务编排层和处理器链。外部三个Provider A/B/C作为外部系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "Orchestrator",
        "Handlers",
        "ExtA",
        "ExtB",
        "ExtC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把PaymentSystem容器画出来，里面放PaymentsController作为REST入口，标注上/payments端点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Controller下面要有个PaymentsService做编排，它不负责具体支付，只协调流程。另外需要一个ProviderSwitcherService来管理链的切换逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Orchestrator",
        "Switcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，PaymentsService和ProviderSwitcherService都标为Service类型。Switcher专门负责链的管理，这个职责拆分很清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Orchestrator",
        "Switcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "核心来了——Handler Chain。需要一个抽象基类PaymentHandler，下面挂三个具体的ProviderHandler，分别对接A、B、C三个外部通道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ChainHandler",
        "HA",
        "HB",
        "HC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "三个Handler都是ProviderHandler的具体实现，只是包装的下游服务不同？结构完全一样？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HA",
        "HB",
        "HC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，结构一致，都是Concrete Handler。HA包装ProviderAService对接ExtA，HB对ExtB，HC对ExtC。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HA",
        "HB",
        "HC",
        "ExtA",
        "ExtB",
        "ExtC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
